T04:39:11.000Z","msg":"post左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec76b6400cd4125e3603d3aa4d9ca9abfb68a41","tid":734012,"uid":121095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T10:52:19.000Z","msg":"FDM 個accuracy 要幾多⋯newton's method 個precision又要幾多⋯<br />\n我之前讀fluid mechanics果陣做過，不過code一早扔哂<br />\n最主要係time 同 spacial derivative 都要discretize 然後每一個time step run一次array"},{"pid":"4dc3b93fc9a0468af8d409c3316d034dd8de4baf","tid":734012,"uid":135278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T11:01:15.000Z","msg":"試下爆power series"},{"pid":"87ae17cf0b8e59f232055b1986a6b3cb663e3b95","tid":734012,"uid":193881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ec76b6400cd4125e3603d3aa4d9ca9abfb68a41","tid":734012,"uid":121095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T10:52:19.000Z","msg":"FDM 個accuracy 要幾多⋯newton's method 個precision又要幾多⋯<br />\n我之前讀fluid mechanics果陣做過，不過code一早扔哂<br />\n最主要係time 同 spacial derivative 都要discretize 然後每一個time step run一次array"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T12:22:42.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個Accuracy 同Precison 隨心, Error 大多都OK, 因為呢D可以後改<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以講多D 個點寫個Flow?<br />\n<br />\n我有boundary conditions 6 條Formula, + 6n 條discretization equation.<br />\n每個time step run 一次newtons method? <br />\n<br />\n我而家既思路係:<br />\n<br />\nInput 拖體parameter 9個<br />\n計出boundary conditions<br />\n得出第一格y(s=0,t=0)<br />\n順序得出y(s=1:n,t=0)<br />\n得出Cable 對拖體影響<br />\n得出新拖體Parameter<br />\nInput 到下個Time step (t=1)<br />\n<br />\n可能有D1999 , 海涵巴打"},{"pid":"8b5b765983ebc1479e8f4454e0e094494df65e79","tid":734012,"uid":193881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dc3b93fc9a0468af8d409c3316d034dd8de4baf","tid":734012,"uid":135278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T11:01:15.000Z","msg":"試下爆power series"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T12:24:37.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPower series 好熟, 似層相識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係個方法係定死左, 我自己定死左自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bebb40224ce56d6941f2e6e7b1276ae7b32afc3f","tid":734012,"uid":121095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87ae17cf0b8e59f232055b1986a6b3cb663e3b95","tid":734012,"uid":193881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ec76b6400cd4125e3603d3aa4d9ca9abfb68a41","tid":734012,"uid":121095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T10:52:19.000Z","msg":"FDM 個accuracy 要幾多⋯newton's method 個precision又要幾多⋯<br />\n我之前讀fluid mechanics果陣做過，不過code一早扔哂<br />\n最主要係time 同 spacial derivative 都要discretize 然後每一個time step run一次array"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T12:22:42.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個Accuracy 同Precison 隨心, Error 大多都OK, 因為呢D可以後改<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以講多D 個點寫個Flow?<br />\n<br />\n我有boundary conditions 6 條Formula, + 6n 條discretization equation.<br />\n每個time step run 一次newtons method? <br />\n<br />\n我而家既思路係:<br />\n<br />\nInput 拖體parameter 9個<br />\n計出boundary conditions<br />\n得出第一格y(s=0,t=0)<br />\n順序得出y(s=1:n,t=0)<br />\n得出Cable 對拖體影響<br />\n得出新拖體Parameter<br />\nInput 到下個Time step (t=1)<br />\n<br />\n可能有D1999 , 海涵巴打"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T14:57:06.000Z","msg":"啱呀個flow <br />\n我試下打唔打到大概既code"},{"pid":"ad18bf578b360dd0c5d7024d3684b85f281add20","tid":734012,"uid":121095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:18:11.000Z","msg":"你知唔知Finite difference 個原理係點？即係forward difference/upwind果d同埋boundary condition有咩criteria? 同埋有機會個scheme唔stable會blow up, even the scheme is correctly implemented 所以你要好清楚用咩scheme去做<br />\n通常簡單d既話, time derivative 會用forward difference, spatial derivative就用central difference, 但係你咁多parameters可能要用d更高order既scheme（唔sure）<br />\n最basic 可以參考下linear advection:<br />\n<a href=\"http://farside.ph.utexas.edu/teaching/329/lectures/node90.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffarside.ph.utexas.edu%2Fteaching%2F329%2Flectures%2Fnode90.html&d=%2BQFYoT12wV6bnFPji%2BooSfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=4e4c2bac\" target=\"_blank\">http://farside.ph.utexas.edu/teaching/329/lectures/node90.html</a><br />\n如果你用forward in time backward in space既話，咁個flow大概係咁：<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\"># Python \n\n# Parameters\nc = 15.0\ndelta_x = 1000.0\nNX = 601\nn = 500\ndelta_t = 30.0\nsigma = c * delta_t / delta_x\n\n# Initialize the array\nu = np.zeros(NX)\nu_next = np.zeros(NX)\nu[NX/2-10:NX/2+10] = 1 #Box signal\n\n# Boundary conditions\nu_next[0] = u[0]\nu_next[NX-1] = u[NX-1]\n\n# Forward-in-time Backward-in-space\nfor i in xrange(n):\n    u_next[1:NX-1] = u[1:NX-1] - sigma * (u[1:NX-1] - u[0:NX-2])\n    u = np.copy(u_next)</code></pre>"},{"pid":"3c2983981ccf13eca2585206116c67134d86a975","tid":734012,"uid":17453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T23:57:26.000Z","msg":"用CFD會唔會solve到？"},{"pid":"e191cda3cc47a6758da6410fcf16a9e0dd00ef39","tid":734012,"uid":193881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ad18bf578b360dd0c5d7024d3684b85f281add20","tid":734012,"uid":121095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:18:11.000Z","msg":"你知唔知Finite difference 個原理係點？即係forward difference/upwind果d同埋boundary condition有咩criteria? 同埋有機會個scheme唔stable會blow up, even the scheme is correctly implemented 所以你要好清楚用咩scheme去做<br />\n通常簡單d既話, time derivative 會用forward difference, spatial derivative就用central difference, 但係你咁多parameters可能要用d更高order既scheme（唔sure）<br />\n最basic 可以參考下linear advection:<br />\n<a href=\"http://farside.ph.utexas.edu/teaching/329/lectures/node90.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffarside.ph.utexas.edu%2Fteaching%2F329%2Flectures%2Fnode90.html&d=%2BQFYoT12wV6bnFPji%2BooSfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=4e4c2bac\" target=\"_blank\">http://farside.ph.utexas.edu/teaching/329/lectures/node90.html</a><br />\n如果你用forward in time backward in space既話，咁個flow大概係咁：<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\"># Python \n\n# Parameters\nc = 15.0\ndelta_x = 1000.0\nNX = 601\nn = 500\ndelta_t = 30.0\nsigma = c * delta_t / delta_x\n\n# Initialize the array\nu = np.zeros(NX)\nu_next = np.zeros(NX)\nu[NX/2-10:NX/2+10] = 1 #Box signal\n\n# Boundary conditions\nu_next[0] = u[0]\nu_next[NX-1] = u[NX-1]\n\n# Forward-in-time Backward-in-space\nfor i in xrange(n):\n    u_next[1:NX-1] = u[1:NX-1] - sigma * (u[1:NX-1] - u[0:NX-2])\n    u = np.copy(u_next)</code></pre>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T02:17:39.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我其實都係參照文獻去做, 個離散方程, 佢地都係用central difference, 見佢地一個二個都Solve 到,某幾個情況比我還要複雜, 所以應該無問題<br />\n<br />\n雖然我唔係好熟Python, 不過都大致理解巴打你段code. <br />\n我想問下你會點寫個BC<br />\n我太耐無寫Program, 有d lost<br />\n我手寫左個BC出黎, 但係唔係好知點樣寫入Matlab<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/10/091530_0b8260d8e99876ffa4ae86f686ee6448.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F10%2F091530_0b8260d8e99876ffa4ae86f686ee6448.jpg&h=e9c41d94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n得出第一格y(s=0,t=0)<br />\n順序得出y(s=1:n,t=0)<br />\n<br />\n呢Part 係咪用Newton method 去計?<br />\n<br />\n我仲整理緊我個思路, 俾FDM 同Newton 攪到好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 坐係到成朝"},{"pid":"0222d166eff49ecc9b2688616599f6bd38e6ad6a","tid":734012,"uid":193881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c2983981ccf13eca2585206116c67134d86a975","tid":734012,"uid":17453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T23:57:26.000Z","msg":"用CFD會唔會solve到？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T02:18:47.000Z","msg":"CFD 係指CFX?<br />\n<br />\n