\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T08:23:29.000Z","msg":"Sor未有電腦係手試唔到 個toolbox唔啱用 因為佢係for一條equation 你個case應該唔會有一個toolbox可以做到 因為你個case係solve緊systems of PDEs 唔只一個variable<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且最重要係boundary condition本身都係要solve equation..而家我會建議你首先整理左以下既野先:<br />\n<br />\n1) boundary conditions既equations<br />\n2) initial conditions, 所有已知既parameters <br />\n<br />\nBtw 我見你話藍字果篇野 佢係有兩個system 一個係個pipe 一個係架船 然後條pipe既boundary condition係由架船既system得出 有無理解錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今晚返去再研究下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T13:00:32.000Z","msg":"好, 等我概括一下我個Design<br />\n我係設計一個數學模型- 無人小型潛艇(AUV)連接一條好很長既光纖到岸上。當中無人小型潛艇既6DOF Model 我已做好, 只差光纖部分<br />\n<br />\n由於光纖係Natural buoyancy, 所以要用到Ablow 提出模疑Cable dynamic既方法 <br />\n<br />\n然而, 成個模型同拖纜系統相似( 大船用纜拖細潛艇) 只不過佢係水上, 我係水下, <br />\n所以係Z.Feng 都會見到同樣既set up (佢Design 都係AUV連CABLE) ,只係 Cable 既boundary condition 稍微不一樣<br />\n<br />\n現是Boundary conditions 如下:<br />\nBC1-3:<br />\n Vc(0,t)= W(2 個cable angle) R( 3 個AUV's angle) (3 個AUV's speed+ 3個AUV 角速度 * 連接點既座標)<br />\n<br />\nBC4-6:<br />\nVc(S,t)=0 由於係Fixed point, 所以最後一點係0位移<br />\n<br />\n** Vc = [Vt, Vn, Vb] **Cable 3個方向速度; S係纜分段(0-S) <br />\n<br />\nInitial conditions 係咪就係BC? 因為我見Z.Feng 都帶過IC=BC<br />\n巴打可以睇下Z. Feng 個篇, 佢無用到Newton method, 佢個Flow 我睇唔明<br />\n<br />\nPS. AUV 既( u, w,v,q,r,.....) 共9個,係已知<br />\n我自己都覺得自己1999, 邊到唔清晰話我知"},{"pid":"9610d40dd22d951518a42e6cc6d9adaacf75f5fd","tid":734012,"uid":193881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ef262f96001f3a853f64fedd055b418be523437","tid":734012,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"92dc2b542d829a4cc6f91cbbf375dc8e99283e6e","tid":734012,"uid":40839,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"7d1b4bf51db50355139845b3022c4b97be3016fa","tid":734012,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T11:40:41.000Z",